 He named Meru Governor Kiraitu Murungi, Senate Deputy Speaker Kithure Kindiki, former Meru Governor Peter Munya, Tharaka Nithi Governor Muthomi Njuki, Meru Senator Mithika Linturi, MPs Kareke Mbiuki and Maoka Maore and himself as some of the potential candidates for Ruto's running mate in 2022.Â 
 "We should bear in mind that no one else but this region will prop our leaders for the national mantle," he said.
